room_title: Escape room "Haunted Deadwood" by Out Of Time Escape in Charlotte
review: So much fun with other couples. Great Great teamwork time and just a different kind of entertainment. Fun room! Excellent and personable customer service. Had a blast!

room_title: Escape room "Haunted Deadwood" by Out Of Time Escape in Charlotte
review: We went to our first one and absolutely loved it! The staff was so friendly and helpful. The room was so detailed and set up so well! I cannot wait to do another one! I would highly recommend coming here!

room_title: Escape room "Haunted Deadwood" by Out Of Time Escape in Charlotte
review: Had a great time. The room was hard (Deadwood) but was still super fun! :-) the staff was very helpful and nice. Will go back.
